421
00:37:25,180 --> 00:37:25,860
Thank you.

422
00:37:27,180 --> 00:37:28,460
What do you think of my painting?

423
00:37:34,700 --> 00:37:35,260
It's good.

424
00:37:37,700 --> 00:37:38,340
Fu Rong.

425
00:37:39,180 --> 00:37:40,420
